---
title: Crispy Tofu Parm with Buttery Zucchini Orzo
description: If breading tofu in Parm and then topping it with melty mozzarella is a crime, then consider us guilty! Served with buttery, garlicky orzo with zucchini and topped with zesty marinara sauce, this will give you all the Italian resto vibes!
